REMARK_EN: The Sept 20, 2015 HWM of 3.473m along with multiple site photos for the day was used to estimate discharge using peak flows from Jun 24, 2012 as a reference.  During the 2012 peak a daily discharge of 306cms and a maximum daily discharge of 373cms were produced.  The noted information and observed scour on the control over the years supports a good estimated discharge max daily for 2015.
